[
    {
        "text": "Now that the pandemic has chased many of us out of our offices,",
        "startTime": -47,
        "endTime": 3661,
        "slowStartTime": 79,
        "slowEndTime": 5717
    },
    {
        "text": "...we're chafing under the new remote rules of work.",
        "startTime": 3777,
        "endTime": 6505,
        "slowStartTime": 5815,
        "slowEndTime": 9982
    },
    {
        "text": "Too much screen time, a lack of boundaries between work and home,...",
        "startTime": 6589,
        "endTime": 10573,
        "slowStartTime": 10033,
        "slowEndTime": 16085
    },
    {
        "text": "...it takes energy to be on,...",
        "startTime": 10935,
        "endTime": 12861,
        "slowStartTime": 16553,
        "slowEndTime": 19517
    },
    {
        "text": "...so, the key to managing remote work is to protect your energy.",
        "startTime": 13013,
        "endTime": 17176,
        "slowStartTime": 19670,
        "slowEndTime": 25989
    },
    {
        "text": "First, pay attention to ritual and routine.",
        "startTime": 17553,
        "endTime": 20501,
        "slowStartTime": 26479,
        "slowEndTime": 30976
    },
    {
        "text": "As much as we hated our commutes,...",
        "startTime": 20669,
        "endTime": 22383,
        "slowStartTime": 31153,
        "slowEndTime": 33799
    },
    {
        "text": "...they were a ritual that created a boundary between work and home.",
        "startTime": 22495,
        "endTime": 25705,
        "slowStartTime": 33893,
        "slowEndTime": 38782
    },
    {
        "text": "So, how can you recreate those breaks and boundaries at home?",
        "startTime": 25859,
        "endTime": 28939,
        "slowStartTime": 38938,
        "slowEndTime": 43633
    },
    {
        "text": "The key is to be intentional.",
        "startTime": 29025,
        "endTime": 30667,
        "slowStartTime": 43687,
        "slowEndTime": 46226
    },
    {
        "text": "It could be music or lighting, a pep talk with a friend.",
        "startTime": 30759,
        "endTime": 35101,
        "slowStartTime": 46289,
        "slowEndTime": 52876
    },
    {
        "text": "You could take a walk around the block at a certain time of day...",
        "startTime": 35318,
        "endTime": 38148,
        "slowStartTime": 53127,
        "slowEndTime": 57447
    },
    {
        "text": "...or even a breathing or stretching routine before you sit.",
        "startTime": 38249,
        "endTime": 41392,
        "slowStartTime": 57523,
        "slowEndTime": 62313
    },
    {
        "text": "Whatever it takes for you to delineate the transition between work and home.",
        "startTime": 41743,
        "endTime": 46947,
        "slowStartTime": 62765,
        "slowEndTime": 70645
    },
    {
        "text": "Second, we need to manage our pace, place and space.",
        "startTime": 47483,
        "endTime": 51734,
        "slowStartTime": 71375,
        "slowEndTime": 77826
    },
    {
        "text": "You could consider the time of day.",
        "startTime": 51912,
        "endTime": 53775,
        "slowStartTime": 78018,
        "slowEndTime": 80888
    },
    {
        "text": "Think about when you can typically summon the energy to be on...",
        "startTime": 53939,
        "endTime": 57671,
        "slowStartTime": 81059,
        "slowEndTime": 86732
    },
    {
        "text": "...and save other times for quiet work.",
        "startTime": 58012,
        "endTime": 60138,
        "slowStartTime": 87168,
        "slowEndTime": 90432
    },
    {
        "text": "For place, use your workspace to help you enforce good boundaries.",
        "startTime": 60380,
        "endTime": 65549,
        "slowStartTime": 90720,
        "slowEndTime": 98549
    },
    {
        "text": "Even if your desk is in your kitchen, make it feel like a workplace.",
        "startTime": 65744,
        "endTime": 70541,
        "slowStartTime": 98766,
        "slowEndTime": 106036
    },
    {
        "text": "For space, build in some alone time everyday...",
        "startTime": 71205,
        "endTime": 75152,
        "slowStartTime": 106958,
        "slowEndTime": 112953
    },
    {
        "text": "...and this includes time away from your kids.",
        "startTime": 75390,
        "endTime": 77215,
        "slowStartTime": 113235,
        "slowEndTime": 116047
    },
    {
        "text": "It's really key to avoiding burnout.",
        "startTime": 77423,
        "endTime": 79462,
        "slowStartTime": 116284,
        "slowEndTime": 119418
    },
    {
        "text": "Finally, if you're a manager, you have a special role to play.",
        "startTime": 79683,
        "endTime": 83474,
        "slowStartTime": 119675,
        "slowEndTime": 125436
    },
    {
        "text": "To help employees protect their pace, place and space.",
        "startTime": 83639,
        "endTime": 87082,
        "slowStartTime": 125608,
        "slowEndTime": 130848
    },
    {
        "text": "Manage the room during video calls.",
        "startTime": 87302,
        "endTime": 89459,
        "slowStartTime": 131103,
        "slowEndTime": 134413
    },
    {
        "text": "Even remotely, chatty extroverts tend to dominate.",
        "startTime": 89713,
        "endTime": 93009,
        "slowStartTime": 134720,
        "slowEndTime": 139738
    },
    {
        "text": "To create a space where everyone can be heard,...",
        "startTime": 93126,
        "endTime": 95419,
        "slowStartTime": 139839,
        "slowEndTime": 143354
    },
    {
        "text": "...structure agendas, assign presentation rules and minimize brainstorming.",
        "startTime": 95586,
        "endTime": 100911,
        "slowStartTime": 143529,
        "slowEndTime": 151592
    },
    {
        "text": "Favor audio over video calls.",
        "startTime": 101297,
        "endTime": 103475,
        "slowStartTime": 152096,
        "slowEndTime": 155437
    },
    {
        "text": "Research shows that we actually communicate more emotion and nuance via audio alone.",
        "startTime": 103686,
        "endTime": 109166,
        "slowStartTime": 155679,
        "slowEndTime": 163974
    },
    {
        "text": "Try asynchronous communication for more complicated or provocative one-on-ones.",
        "startTime": 109389,
        "endTime": 114658,
        "slowStartTime": 164234,
        "slowEndTime": 172212
    },
    {
        "text": "We have an opportunity, remote work is here to stay.",
        "startTime": 114876,
        "endTime": 118148,
        "slowStartTime": 172464,
        "slowEndTime": 177447
    },
    {
        "text": "So, don't just transfer over old habits and old company culture to remote work.",
        "startTime": 118254,
        "endTime": 122964,
        "slowStartTime": 177531,
        "slowEndTime": 184671
    }
]